403
00:32:20.020 --> 00:32:22.022
Jadi, kita berjumpa lagi, Encik Jang.

404
00:32:22.356 --> 00:32:25.192
PENGERUSI JANG YONG-HYEON

405
00:32:26.652 --> 00:32:28.446
Tidak perlu risau tentang saya lagi.

406
00:32:34.743 --> 00:32:37.413
PENGERUSI JANG YONG-HYEON

407
00:33:08.235 --> 00:33:10.029
Hei, ayah. Saya menurunkan Se-hee.

408
00:33:10.112 --> 00:33:11.614
Dia sepatutnya berada dalam penerbangannya sekarang.

409
00:33:13.574 --> 00:33:14.742
Terima kasih.

410
00:33:24.502 --> 00:33:26.879
Pihak pendakwaan telah meletakkan

411
00:33:26.962 --> 00:33:29.798
Timbalan Pendakwa Raya,
Jang Yong-hyeon, Pengerusi S Group

412
00:33:29.882 --> 00:33:31.842
Han Jeong-hun,
Ketua Parti Daehan Pusat

413
00:33:31.926 --> 00:33:34.303
Lee Ju-chan, ketua Daejin Daily

414
00:33:34.386 --> 00:33:36.430
