423
00:33:54.907 --> 00:33:56.825
Kang Sin-jin, bekas Ketua Hakim

424
00:33:56.909 --> 00:33:58.452
di bawah dakwaan pembunuhan
dan hasutannya

425
00:33:58.536 --> 00:33:59.995
